---
title: Italian Pork & Veggie Bolognese with Penne & Parmesan
description: Grating courgette into this easy bolognese sauce gets loads of veggies into dinner. Plus, with all the rich flavours in this dish, the silky baby spinach and secret veggies melt into a perfect meal that the whole family will love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b6d1fd030006c507275eee2-63a4cd0e.jpg
